    Cancellable

    public class FactionCreateEvent
extends CancellableFactionEvent
    When a Faction is created for the first time.

    It is important to note that in order to see who is creating the Faction, you must use

    For a Faction to finish being created, the complete() method must be called. If it is not, the id will not be incremented, the User will not be added to the Faction, and the Faction will not be saved to the database.
